    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Think about any ten unconnected things.  &lt;br&gt;
Connect them all in a half-page story.  &lt;br&gt;
Any human can do this.  &lt;br&gt;
Children can do it better and faster.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A small patch of white clouds in the sky,  &lt;br&gt;
a crow in the nest, a snake crawling to cross the road,  &lt;br&gt;
a man going to home in his cycle,  &lt;br&gt;
the day is Saturday, time is inauspicious Rahukaal,  &lt;br&gt;
man listening to a lovely old song from FM radio.  &lt;br&gt;
What is the connection between all these?  &lt;br&gt;
Who gave meaning to the time that it is good and bad?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
